com.amazonaws.services.s3.model.metrics

Class MetricsFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.services.s3.model.metrics.MetricsFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MetricsFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The filter used to describe a set of objects to include for metrics. The metrics configuration will only include objects that meet the filter's criteria. A filter contains one of MetricsPrefixPredicate, MetricsTagPredicate or MetricsAndOperator.
